  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: cb567088341fa3c4b9b5217e379ebde5, type: 3}
  m_Name: ShopkeeperDialogue_AfterShop
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueText
  speakerName: 'Shopkeeper Tokang '
  lines:
  - So? Fancy anything? Let me know what you're looking for.
  - Hmm...
  - Judging by the looks on your face, it doesn't seem like I have what you're looking
    for.
  - You can try your luck elsewhere, but this place is dangerous, you gotta fight
    to survive.
  - But you already know that, don't you? I saw that you came from the entrance below.
  - Only way you could've reached up here is going through that big guy just below
    us.
  - I don't know if you knocked 'em out, or if you sneaked past 'em. But regardless,
    it ain't no easy feat.
  - Of course that's to be expected from a Box Agent.
  - But this place's a wasteland, don't get too confident. I've seen agents like
    you struggle before.
  - Well, that's enough chit-chatting, if you got any more of those shiny coins to
    spare, I'm all ears.
  - Else, good luck on your journey. I'll be here, ready to make business.
